Name: Run For Coins
About the game: Gameplay Each map has a key that needs to be found to continue, kill all enemies and collect all coins, including hidden ones before the time runs out to get the maximum score of each map. Difficulty increases with each level. Key Features: 16 levels full of enemies and secrets. Collect coins, magic and health Solve puzzles
